Zenith Defy 28800 automatic Swiss made in 1970s


This watch is a collectible item because this watch is part of the first Defy watches produced in very small number by Zenith making them a thought after collectable Zenith watch. This beauty is with you now.


The watch looks perfect and feel elegance on the wrist.


The timepiece is in working order and keep good time


Cosmetic is in good condition with visible traces of use


These are vintage watches, they are not waterproof and have to be handled with care!





The watch has very quality and precise automatic caliber 2562 PC


Sweep second, Date: set by changing 19:30-24 hours, 17 jewels





Stainless steel case


Case diameter: 38 mm w/o crown 41 mm with crown


Case length lug to lug: 45 mm


Modele Depose Pat. no: 493877 - Acier inoxydable


NR 50.038-6


The crown is not original and the crown hasn't a screw locked. (pull push crown) 





The dial is Blue with original Zenith hands and a date (between the 4 and the 5).


The dial has patina and stains


Elegancy design, looks attractive, Central second hand





Stainless steel bracelet and an extra leather strap (in photos) (unbranded so they are not original) 


Lugs width: 22 mm


Bracelet length: 16 cm in close, 22 cm in open





Read the Terms and Conditions and review the photos very carefully before buying.


The watch will be carefully and properly packed and shipped by registered and tracked UPS express or Fedex express for worldwide


Fast and safe shipping. Estimated delivery time: 3-8 business days


Custom fees belongs to the buyers
